Areva CEO Doesn’t Exclude Job Cuts in Germany, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-10-12T04:59:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/areva-ceo-doesn-t-exclude-job-cuts-in-germany-handelsblatt-says.html
Areva SA Chief Executive Officer Luc Oursel doesn’t exclude job cuts in  Germany  as the company
evaluates all options, including stopping some activities in the
country,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing an interview.  Areva will stay in Germany, Oursel told the German
newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
